Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个在"第六感"里面的男孩 他最后死了?\NSo the boy in "The Sixth Sense," he dies at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不 第六感是爱的感觉\NNo, the sixth sense is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-别透剧 -老兄 这电影是十二年前的\N-Guys, spoilers. -The movie's 12 years old, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 你们肯定不会相信\NOh, you're never gonna believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我在药店碰到谁了\Nwho I ran into today at the drugstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一个在买香波的老太太?\NAn old lady buying shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-一个在那个店里工作的人? -是的 而且\N-A guy who works at the drugstore? -Yes. Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,菲茨杰拉尔德先生 我最爱的高中老师\NMr. Fitzgerald, my favorite high school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他酷毙了!\NHe was the coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他老是让我们叫他"艾伦"\NI mean, he used to let us call him "Alan."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫在储物柜里贴了两张照片\NOkay, Dave had two pictures in his locker--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,内维 坎贝尔 和菲茨杰拉尔德先生\NNeve Campbell and Mr. Fitzgerald.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我们知道了\N-He taught us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,连环画也和小说一样有文学性\Nthat comic books were just as literary as novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是穿着凉鞋来上课\NHe wore sandals to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 又来了 还有他的死亡诗社\NOkay, pump the brakes, Dead Poets Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾给我说过:"戴夫 追寻你的梦想\NHe used to say to me, "Dave, Chase your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让你的梦想来追你"\NDon't let your dreams Chase you."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道了 他触动了（摸了）你\NWe get it. He touched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的? 这不是你的错 戴夫 这不是你的错\NReally? It's not your fault, Dave. Dave, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别用"心灵捕手"那套\NStop "Good Will Hunting" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别再拿我和罗宾 威廉姆斯的电影时代相比了\NIn fact, stop comparing me to Robin Williams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来呀 开张了\Nmovies period. Come on. It just opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在干嘛呢?\NWhat's happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是一家新开张的咖啡店 尼克咖啡与茶 很好\NIt's a new coffee shop. Nick's coffee&TEA. NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,附近的人都可以有个好的喝咖啡的店了\Nthe neighborhood could use a good coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是一个店而是一个连锁店\NIt's not a shop. It's a chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们仅在西海岸就开了三百多家\NWe got over 300 stores on the west coast alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莱克斯 一家咖啡连锁店\NAlex, a coffee chain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一个明确的中产阶级标志\Nis a clear indication of gentrification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道那意味着什么吗 -南瓜拿铁咖啡\NDo you know what that means? Pumpkin lattes, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那意味着我们的房租会涨 意味着有机食品店\Nit means our rent goes up. It means organic grocery stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,意味着家庭 戴夫  家庭\NIt means families, Dave. Families.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,刚出炉的脱脂小面包!\NWarm buttermilk scones!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莱克斯 你们所有人都该把这件事放在心上\NAlex, you of all people should be concerned about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一家连锁店是头号大敌\NA chain store is the number one enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对于像你自己这样的小商户来说\Nof a small business owner like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗? 你是对的\N-You know what? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没想过这些\NI never really thought about that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗 我的第一杯咖啡是\NYou know, the first coffee I ever had
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在菲茨杰拉尔德先生的课上\Nwas in Fitzgerald's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我们讨论名著时喝的\NHe let us drink it during great books discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 让我在这个杯子人身上\NOkay, show me on the Cupman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他是摸了（触动）你那儿\Nwhere he touched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福终点站\N第一季 第09集\N ==深影字幕组==
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-戴夫 这三明治是香蕉口味的 -多谢 彭\N-Dave, this sandwich is bananas. -Thanks, Pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望生意能够好起来 知道吗?\NI just wish business would pick up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 成功是需要时间的\N-Well, success takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,B-52s的漫步也不是一天就写好的\N"Roam" by the B-52s wasn't written in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你知道你知道你该做点什么宣传吗?\NHey you know what you should do for publicity?
