Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的   -我做的三明治还不是很好\N-Yeah.  - My sandwiches aren't flashy enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不像那个该死的蚌米货车\Nnot like that damn banh mi truck
