Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能! 是菲茨杰拉尔德先生\NNo way! Mr. Fitzgerald!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-叫我艾伦 -艾伦 还是这么兴奋\N-Call me Alan. -Alan. Still a thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴你决定过来 当然\NI'm so glad you decided to come by. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得我高中的朋友彭妮  哈茨? 嘿!\NUh, you remember my friend Penny Hartz from high school? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么会忘记呢?\NHow I could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前很极端和被人误会\NYou were so intense and misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前是 是的\NI really was. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那么...这个是给你的 - 哦?\N- So... This is for you. - Oh?
