Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不该叫我的名字\NYou shouldn't have said my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会拿把弹簧刀?!\NWhy do you have a switchblade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我没找到我的枪\N<i>because I couldn't find mygun.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怕\NWeird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,事实证明 戴夫的英雄 菲茨杰拉尔德先生\NSo it turns out, Dave's hero, Mr. Fitzgerald,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是个不折不扣的酒鬼 可是戴夫却不明白\Nis a full-on douche, and Dave can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮!\NPenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能没有你!我要让所有人都知道!\NI can't live without you! I want everybody to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,艾伦!我说过我再也不想跟你一起出去了\NAlan! I told you I don't want to go out with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等 等等 等等 等等\NWait, Wait, Wait, Wait, Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你写了首诗\NI wrote you a poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它叫做...\NIt's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"你能给我个碳烤奶酪三明治吗?"\N"Can you make me a grilled cheese sandwich?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝醉了?才上午10点\NAre you drunk? It's 10:00 a.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等下! 等下! 等下!\NHold on! hold on! hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟你说件非常重要的事\NI need to speak with you about something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好 什么事? -到底怎么了?\NOkay. What? -What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 艾伦 从我的走廊上滚出去\N<i>Oh, Alan, get out of my hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你 滚出我的走廊!\NYou leave my hallway!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我们一起走!跟我一起去马达加斯加\N<i>Hey,you leave the hallway! And come with me to Madagascar.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 快走\NNo. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不!你该醒醒了\Nno! You need to sober up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,接着去为戴夫做卷心菜色拉 好吗?\Nand get to work on that slaw for Dave, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快餐车赛四小时后就要开始了\N<i>The truckies are in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的快餐车!\NTruck the truckies!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在说的是我俩  在一起\NThis is about me and you hanging out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还可以给我开张支票，1000块最好\Nand you writing me a check for, like, a Grand tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 谁在乎别人怎么想?\NBesides, who cares about anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫 在乎 好吗\NDave cares, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他太关注你和你的想法了\NHe cares so much about you and your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 很显然 你很关心这个叫戴夫的\NOkay. Obviously, you're very concerned about this Dave guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对 -我想让你知道我\NYeah. -I want you to know that I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以3P\Ntotally open to a 3-way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\NOh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,撞到了我的鸡鸡\NThat was my penis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫对这家伙盲目的追随\NDave has always had a blind spot for that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢他 我不信任老师\NI don't like him. I do not trust teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是不愿发成绩单的老师\Nwho refuse to give out letter grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我懂了 我们都是祖国的花朵\NI mean, I get it. We're all snowflakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们中的一些\Nbut some of us are
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是更好，更聪明的花朵\Nbetter, smarter snowflakes who studied for the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是那种女孩 我知道\N<i>She was that girl in high school. I know.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这个重要的面试\NSo I got my resume all laminated and updated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的简历更新还裹了塑-这是我的简历\N<i>for the big interview. -This is my resume
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,开些玩笑 比方说"你被P90X击中了吗"\NCouple of jokes, couple of "You been hittin' the P90X?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当他说不懂P90X是什么的时候 我就会说\NThen when he doesn't know what the P90x is, I'm like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"老兄 你现在就被击中了"\N<i>"Bro, you gotta hit the P90X now."</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后套套近乎 就得到了这份工作\NThen just some dude stuff, then I get the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 真的吗?\NOh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是 -你能告诉我这四种豆子的区别吗?\NYep. Can you tell the difference between all four of these beans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,它们差别可大了去了- 都是做咖啡的\N'cause they could not be more different. -They are all coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说的话 它们更应该不同\N<i>So in that sense, they could be more different.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是魅力所在  - 那你会雇佣谁?\NYeah. Who would you hire? That's the charm right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,噢!我才不在乎\NOoh! I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 阿莱 我能跟你说句话吗?\NHey, Al. Could I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,马克斯 你为抗议活动做好准备了吗?\NMax, you ready for the protest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 充分准备好了 关于抗议-\NYeah. Totally. About that-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把它取消然后去看电影\Nlet's cancel it and go see a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得.特拉弗斯告诉我有一部新上映的\NThere's a new one out that Peter Travers says
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做"密室逃脱"\Nis a "Stage 5 thrill-icane."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,认真点 我们得出发了\N-Let's get serious. We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我已经做了大量调查\NActually, I've also been doing a ton of research,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,结果显示\Nand it turns out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那家尼克咖啡厅是个非常不错的公司\Nthat Nick's coffee is a super cool company,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我以前不知道\Nwhich I did not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们资助非洲儿童大量物资\Nand they give a ton of money to African kids
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们还把难民接到博卡\Nand they're, like, flying out all these refugees to Boca--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你彻底把我打败了\NAll right, you beat it out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在和那家的店主约会 他真的很酷\NI'm dating the owner Ian. He's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我正处在一个典型的男性困境\NI'm in a serious "You've got male" situation--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"男人"拼做"男" "人"\N"Male" Spelled m-a-l-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信\NI can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这就像是让人困惑的文字游戏\NI know. It's dazzling wordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是彼得.特拉弗斯\NI'm the Peter Travers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在男同性恋关系中挣扎\Nof complicated gay relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是个叛徒 - 你知道..我也是个叛徒\NI'm also a sellout. -Well, you know... I'm a sellout, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见这些标语了吗?\NYou see these signs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我从一些官员那儿拿到这些广告板\NI got the poster boards at office plus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这些价格贵的离谱! -我知道\NThe prices are unreal!  -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你不会生我的气?-不!你就像个小男孩\NSo you're not mad at me? -No! You like a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是叛徒最滑稽的地方\NThat is totally the funnest thing to sell out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最棒的-你就像个小男孩!你就像个小男孩!\NYou're the best. -you like a boy! You like a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你这么快就变成最坏的了\Nand now you're the worst very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 嗯 我们现在就终止抗议\NOkay, Well, we have to stop this protest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把时间都省给爱\Nand save the day for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 哇 哇 我从没说过是爱\NWhoa, whoa, whoa. I never said anything about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,得了 为了爱 为了爱\NCome on. For love! For love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为了喜欢 为了喜欢!\NFor like.Like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 戴夫?-嘿!\NWhat up, Dave? -Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,腌泡汁闻起来不错\NThat marinade smells amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们迫不及待的看你去赢了 -我这就去\NWe're all so psyched to see you kick ass at the truckies. -I'm almost ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是在等一会艾伦来为我做卷心菜色拉\NI'm just waiting on Alan to get here to make the slaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这没什么大不了的\NBut it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他只迟到了半小时 但是..\NHe's just a few half-hours late, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫 我想让你知道...\NDave, I just want you to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的三明治\Nyou've got a really great sandwich
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,即使不配沙拉也是美味\Nwith or without that slaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就有卷心菜色拉了 为什么没有了?\NThere's gonna be slaw. Why wouldn't there be slaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的是 艾伦今天可能不会来了\NWhat I'm trying to say is, Alan might not come today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他可能没你想想的那么完美\Nbecause he may not be as great of a guy as you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮 我知道你想说什么\NPenny, I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我和艾伦谈过了\NAll right, I talked to Alan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你很受伤因为你刚刚和他分手 -什么?\NYou're just hurt because he broke it off with you. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 想我和他这样的人思想很自由\NYeah, guys like me and him are free spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我们任思想漫游\NYou know, we gotta be free to roam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们自由自在的...\NWe gotta be free to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是见鬼了 我发誓我再也不会这么做\N<i>That is so weird. I promise I will never do that again.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫你跟艾伦不同 好不好?\NDave, you are nothing like Alan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个酒鬼 身无分文 还是个蠢货\NHe's a douche who's broke, and he's stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他不知道你到底有多棒\Nbecause he doesn't realize how awesome you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道我有多优秀 好吗?\N<i>He does realize how awesome I am, okay?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定会来的\NAnd he's gonna be at the truckies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这对你很难接受的话 那你可以不用来了\NAnd if that's too weird for you, then maybe you shouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 你宁愿他站在这儿而不是我?\NWow. You'd rather have him there than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 彭 只是..色拉在他手上\NNo. Pen. It's just... he's bringing the slaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 菲茨杰先生--艾伦!\NHey, Mr. Fitzg--Alan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想打扰你做事\NDon't want to tie you down,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来确认沙拉的事\Nbut I'm just calling to check on the slaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我现在要去准备了\NUm, I'm gonna go set up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我会把这些东西都留给你\Nbut I'm gonna leave everything here for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以自己进来做些你喜欢的东西\Nand you can just let yourself in and do your thang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望能见到你 好的 爱你\NReally hope to see ya, all right. Love ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯--不 只是--想你\NJust--no, that--miss ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗?你加油就行\NYou know what? You just keep on truckin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 凯文和斯蒂文\NOkay, Kevin and Steve,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是工商管理硕士 真的非常让人惊讶\Nyou both have MBAs. That's really impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德 嗯 你没有提交简历\NBrad. Uh, you didn't hand in a résumé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是有什么原因吗? 这...\NAny reason for that? This...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\Nhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我脸上有什么东西吗?\NUh, do I have something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的简历是--\NHere's my résumé--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我 咱们可以一起去吃牛排\Nyou, me, couple of steaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,或者看（NBA）公牛的比赛\Nbulls game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-还是去打打棒球吗? -我可以理解成\N-I don't know. Batting cages? -So I'm gonna take that as a "No."
